{"tid":712351,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"美斯嫂撐老公笑門將係蠢才","createTime":"2018-06-22T04:41:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T04:52:08.000Z","uid":33799,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"476e683fb17afe69adc9031c1cb5a869f41881e4","tid":712351,"uid":33799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T04:41:18.000Z","msg":"美斯太太安東妮娜在社交網站貼相支持老公，還附和網民批評教練森柏奧利是蠢才的言論，表示門將也一樣。<br />\n<br />\n阿根廷周四分組賽不敵克羅地亞0:3，晉級形勢岌岌可危，美斯的妻子安東妮娜（Antonela Roccuzzo）賽前已經張貼兒子穿藍白球衣的打氣相，賽後又張貼美斯的相片寫上：「Always with you！」的字句，希望美斯和球隊不要放棄，爭取最後一場擊敗尼日利亞博出線。 不少網民都紛紛留言，<span style=\"color: red;\">Behar Issa寫道：「那個教練是個蠢才&hellip;&hellip;永遠支持美斯！」安東妮娜不但「like」對方的講法，還留言：「那個門將也是！」還加上「笑到喊」的Emoji</span>。阿根廷門將韋利卡巴尼路一個解圍失誤，令克羅地亞先開紀錄，是球隊輸波最大罪人。 Edwain Peter則表示那不是支持球隊與否的問題，問題是阿根廷的中場形同虛設。看來，安東妮娜的網友都是足球專家，留言都非常有水準。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://emojipedia-us.s3.amazonaws.com/thumbs/120/apple/129/face-with-tears-of-joy_1f602.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Femojipedia-us.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fthumbs%2F120%2Fapple%2F129%2Fface-with-tears-of-joy_1f602.png&h=616476d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"760222ffe284451d1b175e06bb3f47189a12ddb4","tid":712351,"uid":33799,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T04:42:27.000Z","msg":"當「救世主」Messi沒有如預期般挺身而出時，阿根廷首都布宜諾斯艾利斯的球迷區陷入一片寂靜，他們只能驚恐地瞪著螢幕，直到比賽終場響哨。<br />\n<br />\n「我們輸得太慘了，對方這次徹底羞辱了我們。」22歲的球迷Joaquin悲痛地說：「現在，我們只能把希望寄託在對決奈及利亞了。」<br />\n<br />\n經歷0比3的慘敗，阿根廷唯一晉級的希望就是打贏奈及利亞，剩下的還有祈禱其他賽事結果能對他們有利，不過即使是最死忠的球迷，他們現在也不敢抱任何希望。<br />\n<br />\n阿根廷陣中最受批評的中心人物當然還是Lionel Messi，他遠低於水準的表現讓大家失望。「Messi明明都帶領西甲巴塞隆納不斷贏球，但他帶給我們的卻只有敗仗和悲傷。」50歲的球迷Miguel Angel Gutierrez頭上頂著阿根廷隊的爆炸帽，生氣地說。<br />\n<br />\n臉上畫著天藍白國旗彩繪的球迷，原先應該在布宜諾斯艾利斯歡樂的開派對慶祝，現在的氣氛卻像在劇院看恐怖電影。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/HkPUUQ22qHOnrpDihIjnRw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/tsna_2018__196/0190960cdab3639e06eb79c25a0a7af4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FHkPUUQ22qHOnrpDihIjnRw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Ftsna_2018__196%2F0190960cdab3639e06eb79c25a0a7af4&h=b96ef1e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"66eb7e71276e793ff14e6232c0a3202cd29523e9","tid":712351,"uid":14423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T04:44:24.000Z","msg":"堅定流呀，咁串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"873279de0b200c84ea5a9ce1306cbfddf5c79ad5","tid":712351,"uid":33799,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"66eb7e71276e793ff14e6232c0a3202cd29523e9","tid":712351,"uid":14423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T04:44:24.000Z","msg":"堅定流呀，咁串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T04:47:53.000Z","msg":"其實係fan page 唔係本人"},{"pid":"46d21e6d84aa591c76e12c9cb6d45e5175ecb9d1","tid":712351,"uid":14423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"873279de0b200c84ea5a9ce1306cbfddf5c79ad5","tid":712351,"uid":33799,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"66eb7e71276e793ff14e6232c0a3202cd29523e9","tid":712351,"uid":14423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T04:44:24.000Z","msg":"堅定流呀，咁串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T04:47:53.000Z","msg":"其實係fan page 唔係本人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T04:52:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}